{"title":"“半仙”失算（图片）","authors":["飞天"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":2,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“半仙”失算"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞天摄于江苏淮安市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时逢过大年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上街来摆摊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中暗自揣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看相把钱骗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清茶泡一杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香烟手中燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投下香饵钩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专等鱼来衔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不料世风转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卦摊遭冷淡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无人信天命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半仙失了算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶冷烟熄灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收摊心不甘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无奈睡意袭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当街打起鼾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此君当早醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夕非往年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文明春风起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷信快收摊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——编辑附语"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}